@startuml claw-compactor-sequence-claw
title Claw — single pipeline pass (with auto-checkpoint at 100k tokens)
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "JetBrains Mono"
skinparam sequenceArrowColor #444

actor User
participant "opencode\nsession" as OC
participant "claw\nagent" as Claw
participant "claw-compactor\nplugin" as Plugin
database  ".compactor/" as Disk
participant "LiteLLM\n(extractor)" as LLM

User -> OC : "/agents claw\ncompact"
OC -> Claw : start session
Claw -> Disk : read knowledge/{tool-catalog,prospect-index,a2a-acp-index}.json\n(seed discovery)
Claw -> Disk : read sessions/<sid>/plan.json (if present)

== Step 1 — Discover ==
Claw -> Claw : run 9 scanners\n(compose, mcp, skills, env, scripts, arch,\nhealth, litellm, process)
Claw -> Disk : write registry/integrations.<ts>.json
Plugin <-- OC : every tool.execute.after\n(buffered per sessionID)

== Step 2 — Classify ==
Claw -> Claw : rules first (PLAN.md §5)
Claw -> Claw : LLM tie-break only on miss

== Step 3 — Detect ==
Claw -> Claw : 5 axes: merge | prune | collapse | rebudget | mcp-dedupe

== Step 4 — Draft ==
Claw -> Disk : write drafts/<op-id>/

== Step 5 — Log ==
Claw -> Disk : append log.jsonl
Claw -> Disk : append summaries/YYYY-MM-DD.md

== Step 5.5 — Registry + Neo4j ==
note over OC, Plugin
  claw-compactor plugin is not configured for claw.
  claw persists discovery explicitly via registry + graph sync.
end note
Claw -> Disk : write registry/integrations.<ts>.json
Claw -> Neo4j : sync-from-compactor --session <sid> --registry <path>
Neo4j --> Claw : Tool / Evidence / RegistrySnapshot graph
Claw -> Neo4j : MATCH (t:Tool) RETURN count(t)

== Step 6 — Exit ==
Claw -> User : print summaries/YYYY-MM-DD.md path

@enduml
